{% comment %}
  Don't forget to compress your icons! https://jakearchibald.github.io/svgomg/
  All icons must be created at 32px by 32px regardless of size to be scaled to

  - - - VARIABLES - - -

  - size: The icon size, if square (set to auto for custom CSS sizing)
  - viewbox: Set to false to disable the SVG viewbox element
  - name: Icon title which overrides the default name
{% endcomment %}

